data.description: Perched atop a beautiful 1+ acre corner lot in Darlington Ridge, this home offers curb appeal and single level living.  Split floor plan w/hardwood floors throughout living, kitchen & dining areas plus convenient drop zone near garage.  Tons of kitchen cabinetry w/bar & breakfast nook.  Primary bath features tile shower, garden tub & double sink vanity.  Cozy deck & patio in the rear.  Not far from the convenience of downtown Rutherfordton or access to US-221 Hwy & I-40.
